              p.about_text01_en <span class="ls_01">NEXTVIEW</span> Labels is dedicated to breathing new life into classical music, focusing on the ambient, chill, and post-classical genres. While we hold traditional classical music in high regard, we’re not afraid to push its boundaries, constantly striving to create innovative and fresh musical styles. Our roster at <span class="ls_01">NEXTVIEW</span> Labels consists of artists who are deeply passionate and committed to their craft. Together, we aim to share our music and the emotions it evokes with audiences worldwide, creating lasting connections that endure… now and always.
